<p><font color="#669900"><b>Konqueror - More Than a Web Browser</b></font></p>
<p>Konqueror is your helper for your daily work, providing numerous functions for performing file operations and maintaining order. For example, you can generate an index file for your image collection.</p>
<p>Konqueror is a full-fledged web browser and disk jockey for audio CDs. The Kget plug-in facilitates downloads. Advanced users will appreciate the many input and output modules for opening FTP sessions, browsing man and info pages, or using a CVS system.</p>
<p>In addition to Konqueror, SUSE offers a number of other Open Source web browsers such as Mozilla, Epiphany for GNOME users, and the browser Links for the command line.</p>
